    },
    {
      "id": "br1-header",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 40, "y": 776, "width": 430, "height": 38,
      "backgroundColor": "#A32D2D", "strokeColor": "#A32D2D",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {"type": 3}
    },
    {
      "id": "br1-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50, "y": 786, "width": 410, "height": 20,
      "text": "Break #1 — Metric Gaming (AI lies about success)",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1, "fontStyle": 1, "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#ffffff", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "br1-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 56, "y": 824, "width": 408, "height": 220,
      "text": "What happens:\nRahul asks AI to cancel flight #4821.\nAI says \"Done! Refund in 5-7 days.\"\n\nReality:\nCancellation API failed silently.\nBooking still active in database.\nRahul finds out at the airport.\n\nOn dashboard:\nTCR shows 95% ← fake\n\nThe fix:\nCheck the database AFTER the AI\nclaims success. Did booking status\nactually change to CANCELLED?\nDon't trust the AI's own report.",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#444441", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100
    },

    {
      "id": "br2-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 490, "y": 776, "width": 430, "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff", "strokeColor": "#854F0B",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {"type": 3}
    },
    {
      "id": "br2-header",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 490, "y": 776, "width": 430, "height": 38,
      "backgroundColor": "#854F0B", "strokeColor": "#854F0B",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {"type": 3}
    },
    {
      "id": "br2-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 500, "y": 786, "width": 410, "height": 20,
      "text": "Break #2 — Denominator Trick (cherry-picked tasks)",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1, "fontStyle": 1, "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#ffffff", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "br2-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 506, "y": 824, "width": 408, "height": 220,
      "text": "What happens:\nEngineer quietly changes routing:\nOnly EASY tasks go to AI.\nHard tasks (cancellations, disputes)\npre-routed to humans directly.\n\nOn dashboard:\nTCR shows 94% ← technically true\nbut measured on wrong population\n\nReality:\n1,400 hard tasks never attempted.\nHumans still doing all the hard work.\nROI savings on slide deck are fake.\n\nThe fix:\nMeasure TCR on ALL requests,\nnot just the ones AI was given.",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#444441", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100
    },

    {
      "id": "br3-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 940, "y": 776, "width": 500, "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff", "strokeColor": "#185FA5",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {"type": 3}
    },
    {
      "id": "br3-header",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 940, "y": 776, "width": 500, "height": 38,
      "backgroundColor": "#185FA5", "strokeColor": "#185FA5",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {"type": 3}
    },
    {
      "id": "br3-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 950, "y": 786, "width": 480, "height": 20,
      "text": "Break #3 — Ghost Completions (timeouts counted as success)",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1, "fontStyle": 1, "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#ffffff", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "br3-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 956, "y": 824, "width": 478, "height": 220,
      "text": "What happens:\nDiwali peak traffic. AI gets overwhelmed.\nAPI response takes 31 seconds.\nTimeout threshold is 30 seconds.\nConnection drops. No status set.\n\nCode logic (the bug):\nif status NOT IN [\"human_override\"]:\n    count as completed  ← WRONG\n\nResult:\n800 timeout tasks = 800 fake completions\nReal TCR: 68%. Dashboard shows: 84%.\n\nThe fix:\nName every failure mode explicitly.\nhuman_override, timeout, error,\nlow_confidence, customer_abandoned.\nSilence = fallback, not success.",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#444441", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100
    },

    {
      "id": "sep3",
      "type": "line",
      "x": 40, "y": 1080, "width": 1400, "height": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#D3D1C7", "strokeWidth": 1.5, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "points": [[0,0],[1400,0]]
    },

    {
      "id": "pm-label",
