      "x": 50, "y": 1172, "width": 300, "height": 88,
      "text": "FAQ answers:     91% ✓\nFlight booking:  79% ⚠\nCancellations:   58% ✗\n\nOverall = 82% looks fine.\nCancellations = crisis. Fix that first.",
